Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.67,0:00:03.83,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Alibis, codes, tricks, deals.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.50,0:00:06.17,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The mysterious Black Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.73,0:00:08.50,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today's stage is a party venue!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.50,0:00:09.76,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}VIPs, watch your backs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.09,0:00:11.63,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.63,0:00:13.60,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.60,0:00:15.52,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.80,0:01:40.55,Title,,0,0,0,,The Mysterious Sniper Murder Case\N(Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:53.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been giving us a headache!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.12,0:01:56.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.06,0:01:56.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.91,0:01:59.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though it was a long line...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.99,0:02:02.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That nice man let me get some food first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.08,0:02:05.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who's talking with the sumo elder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.26,0:02:07.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the president of a dye company.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.58,0:02:09.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know him, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:10.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.95,0:02:12.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at his fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.25,0:02:13.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fingers?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.59,0:02:17.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're in contact with dyes every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.68,0:02:20.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your fingers and even your\Nnails will be stained by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:24.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But wouldn't the dye workers fit the description, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.10,0:02:27.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you know that he's the president?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.05,0:02:29.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at the difference between\Nhis left and his right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.65,0:02:33.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His right is tanned but his left isn't, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.53,0:02:37.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, he likely plays a lot of golf.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.16,0:02:41.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he didn't go golfing very often, the\Ndifference wouldn't be as glaring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:45.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he were just an employee, he\Nwouldn't get to play so often...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.66,0:02:47.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which is what makes him the president?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.30,0:02:48.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:50.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:53.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I get your autograph, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.83,0:02:56.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a huge fan of yours, Kaze Kabuto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-zeki{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.83,0:02:56.88,Signs,,0,0,0,,"Zeki" is an honorific used for sumo wrestlers, more so than "-san"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.85,0:02:59.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Kaze Iwato!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:03.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.61,0:03:11.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That scared the hell out of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.47,0:03:14.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hard to tell sumo wrestlers\Napart without their loincloths.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:17.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, I might as well not get an autograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:24.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.15,0:03:26.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're embarrassing us—don't eat so loudly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:30.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone gave me a ticket to this\Nparty in place of my service fee!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:32.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be a waste if I don't eat what it's worth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.01,0:03:35.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri Kogoro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:36.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:40.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Tanaka Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.89,0:03:43.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you spare me some of your time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:46.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:47.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My time is all yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.59,0:03:49.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can get married as well if you'd like!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:52.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:54.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure thing, I'm fine with anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.99,0:04:00.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, you're a company president?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:07.87,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Ishimoto Seiji (54)\NIshimoto Precision Device\NRepresentative Director
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:01.86,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:07.83,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I produce and sell precision devices found\Nmainly in airplanes and computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:10.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, what did you want me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.49,0:04:11.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tanaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:12.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:15.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To be honest, our president has received a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:16.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A threat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:22.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"You've lost whatever value you have left as a person."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:24.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'll make sure to kill you myself."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:27.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, we'd like you to find out who did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.52,0:04:29.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:30.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know that person over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.69,0:04:32.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guy on the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:36.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guy who handed out his business\Ncard looks like an important person...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:38.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And yet he's bowing profusely to the other man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.56,0:04:40.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think the man on the left is considered superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.83,0:04:51.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The way I see it, I think he's the\Nson of some rich monopoly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:53.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:58.75,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Niikura Tsuneaki (32)\NParliamentarian Secretary
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:58.05,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,He's probably the secretary of some\Nwell-known politician, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.93,0:05:01.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.47,0:05:03.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for the person over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.56,0:05:06.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think he belongs here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:09.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the moment he stepped in,\Nhe's been spying on everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:12.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He isn't here to enjoy the party at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:13.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's his profession?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:19.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have feuds with certain individuals?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:20.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:23.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then, why haven't you contacted the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.87,0:05:26.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The president has never been too fond of the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:32.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, the police won't take the matter\Nseriously until something has come of it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.04,0:05:36.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a difficulty inherent in their protocol...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:39.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, you seem quite knowledgeable about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.01,0:05:43.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not only do I understand the\Npolice, but you as well, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:47.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I specifically chose you for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:48.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:52.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After searching through my computer, I decided\Nthat Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was definitely the best choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:54.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:57.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll take on this case, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:05:59.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:06:03.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But from now on, I'll need to remain\Nin close contact with Ishimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:07.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it to you to deal with the entire investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:11.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can get closer to Yukiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:13.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:16.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't I take your picture as a souvenir?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, let's take a picture together!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:19.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:21.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:22.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over here's better!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:25.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ready when you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.14,0:06:27.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now say...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:28.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:36.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, I've done nothing that might anger people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.11,0:06:40.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, as a man who has lived for many years...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:44.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's possible I may have unknowingly\Nhurt someone at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:46.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But surely it isn't my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:51.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We will now begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:55.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would like to welcome today's guest\Nto share a few words with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:59.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takada Masao{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}, member of the\NJapan House of Representatives...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.24,0:07:00.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please come to the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.68,0:07:08.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:12.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see, he really is a parliamentarian secretary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:14.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:15.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you're good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.69,0:07:17.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:20.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was pretty neat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just now, they managed to shine the spotlight\Non him despite how dark it is in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:26.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he was told where to stand beforehand...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:30.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or maybe the spotlight was designed to follow\Nthe microphone on his chest automatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:36.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why isn't he headed straight to the stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:37.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:40.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's demanding everyone's attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:44.29,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.34,0:07:48.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ishimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, please excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:49.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Greetings, thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.43,0:07:54.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:56.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:07:59.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Niikura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:21.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:26.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:35.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.27,0:08:37.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That person got away pretty fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:48.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something terrible has happened to Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:50.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, please contact the committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:56.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's me, Niikura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:59.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ishimoto was threatened by someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:02.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who was aiming for his life, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:03.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:04.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he entrusted me with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:09.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means the bullet that was\Nintended for Ishimoto missed...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.08,0:09:12.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And hit Politician Takada instead, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.05,0:09:13.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that was the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:16.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were many guests present.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:18.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's possible there were some witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.27,0:09:19.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.31,0:09:22.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are the guests now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.03,0:09:24.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, we have them gathered in the next room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:28.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:30.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can you just run off like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.99,0:09:33.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was really nervous, so I went to the restroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:38.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This case doesn't require help from a brat like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:42.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I just saw somebody suspicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:42.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:46.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man had been leaning against\Nthe wall from the beginning, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:49.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right when the gun fired, he went into\Nthe lighting control room up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:51.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the place, it'd be easy to\Ntake aim even among the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.81,0:09:59.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what kind of person was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:01.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:04.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He looks just like a killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:07.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:08.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:09.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.81,0:10:12.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's a picture of someone\Nwho might be the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:14.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:16.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, the killer has to be him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:27.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you can't touch that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:30.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.01,0:10:31.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those are shards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.47,0:10:35.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're from the mini-microphone that\NPolitician Takada was wearing at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.89,0:10:37.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So did the bullet hit the microphone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:39.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That seems to be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's more than enough, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.69,0:10:46.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:47.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He does this whenever I take my eyes off him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, let's wait in the lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:03.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:04.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To the restroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:06.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't hold it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:10.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which restroom would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.93,0:11:19.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was pretty fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:19.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure was!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:27.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She looks pretty anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:30.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who is he, the man with the long hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.42,0:11:51.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.26,0:11:56.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The president just had his life on the line...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.93,0:11:59.06,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And yet she went out discreetly just to meet this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:01.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Something doesn't look right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:19.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the police interrogation is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:21.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like to go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:25.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ishimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the injury you\Nsuffered may not be much, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:27.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was your life that the killer wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:29.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the police hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.67,0:12:30.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We won't deal with the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:34.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's already a hospital we usually go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.79,0:12:39.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, he should be free to choose\Nwhether to accept police protection or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:42.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:45.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, who's going to protect Ishimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:47.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:48.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.44,0:12:51.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it, I'll promise you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:54.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Starting tonight, I will stay with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:55.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, President, to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:00.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.27,0:13:02.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About the man in this photo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:04.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:09.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We took a look through the guestbook,\Nbut it didn't look like he belonged here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.54,0:13:14.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, we already tightened the security\Naround here, so maybe we'll find something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:16.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for criminal records, those are being investigated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.55,0:13:19.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:20.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:23.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.96,0:13:27.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know which police\Nhospital he's supposed to go to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:29.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He says he hates the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.06,0:13:33.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Starting today, I'm staying with\NYukiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} as their bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:34.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:37.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Better stay away from this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.44,0:13:39.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:43.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a splendid car!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:48.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yukiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, why don't you sit here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.66,0:13:52.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For safety reasons, don't you think we\Nshould sit on either side of the president?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:55.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess so, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:13:57.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be good and go home with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:07.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see, the subway is over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:10.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:19.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There were a lot of guests in the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:22.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If someone wanted to shoot\Nlshimoto{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}, it'd be fairly difficult...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.03,0:14:25.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Unless they were a professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.67,0:14:40.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What are those marks?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:42.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}An adhesive substance and new scratches?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.18,0:14:45.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why would there be something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:47.38,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.02,0:14:50.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Microphone shards...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:14:53.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The lighting control room is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:04.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:06.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This doesn't look like a hospital room...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:09.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's more like a hotel suite!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:13.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, your room will be the one\Nwe just passed through, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.75,0:15:16.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since there's only one path between the two rooms...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:22.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If someone were to come in here, they'd\Nhave to go through your room first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:23.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:26.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As expected of you, Yukiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.25,0:15:28.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You even thought about how to make the room safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:30.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:33.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The president has been running\Nour company by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:36.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If something happened to our president,\Nthe company would be done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:41.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Yukiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, where\Nwill you be staying tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:43.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's only one bed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:45.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going home to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.64,0:15:48.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because now Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is\Nhere to guard the president!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.66,0:15:50.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:51.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:55.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:56.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This room is pretty nice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.49,0:15:58.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be counting on you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:01.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll try my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:03.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,President, how's your treatment going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:07.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Piece of cake, just a little scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tanaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, I'll be counting on you to\Ndeal with the whole Takada thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:14.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll make sure to have it taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.02,0:16:19.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this about Politician Takada?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.48,0:16:22.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's about his funeral and consolation money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:27.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, Politician Takada took the\Nfall for our president this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:28.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I have to deal with those now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:30.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you have to leave then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:36.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My appointment with his secretary\NNiikura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} isn't due until later...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.65,0:16:38.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I can stay with you for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:40.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really now!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.71,0:16:41.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:44.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you want something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.01,0:16:46.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, beer's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:49.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No I mean... cola.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:53.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, may I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.22,0:16:55.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:16:59.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said that you used a computer\Nto choose me for the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.93,0:17:03.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But aside from me, there must've\Nbeen other private detectives, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.86,0:17:05.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you pick me, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:11.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we went by past experience and detective skills,\Nthere'd definitely be a lot of worthy candidates.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:15.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if we wanted someone\Nwith charismatic qualities...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.83,0:17:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the answer is pretty obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:20.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Other than you, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},\Nwho could we possibly pick?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.99,0:17:23.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you've definitely made the right choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:29.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Life is awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.47,0:17:33.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This cola is really tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.04,0:17:33.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A refill, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.85,0:17:41.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.13,0:17:41.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please hold a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.65,0:17:44.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, it's for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.05,0:17:44.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:48.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:51.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, Great Detective Mouri Kogoro speaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.03,0:17:55.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're pretty arrogant, calling\Nyourself "great detective"...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:17:58.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:01.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About the suspicious man who was at the party...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:03.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've managed to find his criminal record.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:04.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:07.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was unbelievable, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.36,0:18:13.92,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hiraoka Shirou (35)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.01,0:18:10.12,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Hiraoka Shirou, age 35.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:13.97,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,He specializes in uncovering trade secrets\Nand then blackmailing for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.39,0:18:17.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Word on the street is that, once he\Ntargets someone, he won't let them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:20.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,People have given him the\Nnickname "Piranha Hiraoka".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:24.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you mean Hiraoka may\Nhave sunk his teeth in this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:24.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.97,0:18:29.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think Ishimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} may have done something\Nthat Hiraoka could use for blackmail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:33.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, judging from Ishimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s\Ncharacteristics, he must've refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.98,0:18:39.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pissed off by this, Hiraoka then attempted\Nto end Ishimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s life, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:54.90,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's unfortunate for you to be glared\Nat by me, Snake{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-sama{\r\be10} the Killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:57.85,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But I'll give you one chance to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:01.85,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}All you have to do is use that to defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:06.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as I wondered where you could've been...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:08.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Turns out you're here watching TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:10.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's time to sleep now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.49,0:19:15.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you hear me, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:16.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm turning it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.48,0:19:16.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:40.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, so that's what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:42.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.06,0:19:47.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The truth is that the true culprit has\Nbeen misleading us the entire time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.73,0:19:50.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What a thoroughly cunning trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.15,0:19:55.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But there just isn't enough evidence\Nat our disposal right now to prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.67,0:20:12.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the phone is ringing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.30,0:20:15.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No good, I fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:18.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.72,0:20:21.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hi, sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:22.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:24.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bad news, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:25.84,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:26.52,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:29.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Hiraoka Shirou guy was found dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.23,0:20:31.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.60,0:20:32.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where was he found!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.36,0:20:38.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He slipped and fell down the\Nstairwell of an abandoned house.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:41.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He hit is head, which became the fatal blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.95,0:20:43.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it an accident, or was it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:45.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.44,0:20:48.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're about to head to the scene now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.03,0:20:50.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I find any leads, I'll let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.96,0:20:53.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The forensics are working on the scene as of now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.85,0:21:07.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.27,0:21:08.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.77,0:21:14.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you mean until you're sure that Ishimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nis going to be all right, you can't come home?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.49,0:21:17.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.99,0:21:22.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did Uncle call just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.91,0:21:23.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.73,0:21:29.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, the picture we took was of a guy named Hiraoka,\Nwho was suspected of sniping at Ishimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.82,0:21:31.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he was found dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:33.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be a murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.21,0:21:36.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.08,0:21:37.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because he fell down some stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.22,0:21:40.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They say he was hiding in the\Nbuilding when he lost his footing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.83,0:21:42.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And fatally injured his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.43,0:21:45.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No, this wasn't an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.27,0:21:49.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If my hypothesis is correct, this is a murder case!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.98,0:21:54.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The real culprit killed Hiraoka\Nbecause he knew the secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.02,0:21:59.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This case, a series of events that began with\Nlshimoto{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} receiving a death threat...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.36,0:22:02.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}May appear easily solved at first, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.60,0:22:05.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In reality, the stunning truth has yet to be revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.74,0:22:08.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I will definitely find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.20,0:22:11.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}From the pile of complexly tangled threads...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.04,0:22:13.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I will find the thread of truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.22,0:23:56.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, Yukiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} has a\Nboyfriend named Shibata Kenichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.73,0:23:57.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.33,0:24:01.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very well, I will reveal everything to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.90,0:24:04.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The real culprit... is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.74,0:24:09.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.32,0:24:13.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Mysterious Sniper Murder Case (Part 2)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.82,0:24:17.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.52,0:24:19.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remote control
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.08,0:24:20.33,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time, it's Part 2!{Next time is the second chapter.}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.33,0:24:21.87,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What's the title of the new opening theme?{What is the title of the new theme song?}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.87,0:24:22.29,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Tru—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.90,0:24:24.90,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,He bit his tongue.
